headline: Autodesk extends invitation to join financial results conference call
summary: Autodesk, Inc. (NASDAQ: ADSK) today announced it will share its fourth quarter fiscal 2025 financial results conference call via its website on Thursday, February 27, 2025, at 2 p.m. Pacific Time. Join the live webcast call here: autodesk.com/investors. An audio replay of the webcast will be available after 5 p.m. PT at autodesk.com/investors.
